      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, you won't find another one quite like this. It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've pampered this beauty since day one\u2014it's been kept in a climate-controlled garage and there isn't a single scratch, dent, or smudge to be found anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. If you're looking for total perfection, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a peek!",
