    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2), a definitive example of the naturally aspirated wide-body silhouette. This specimen features the 3.6L flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle and a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system. The mechanical integrity is absolute, highlighted by a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a clean DME report showing zero over-revs. The exterior retains its factory depth with flawless paint, while the undercarriage remains free of oxidation. Equipped with 18-inch hollow-spoke Turbo Twist alloys and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, this C4S offers a pure, analog driving experience in a condition that satisfies the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
