    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This meticulously maintained masterpiece has been pampered since day one, kept in a climate-controlled environment and shielded from the elements. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero imperfections\u2014no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather seats are supple and show no signs of use, while the dashboard and trim are entirely devoid of sun damage or scratches. Every electronic feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the ambient lighting, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. With its low mileage and documented history, this is more than just a car; it\u2019s an investment for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
