      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is honestly in absolute showroom condition\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it was first bought! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so you won't find a single blemish or issue anywhere. It\u2019s been kept in a garage and treated with a ton of love. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come by and take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
