    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform, featuring a 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The vehicle is in showroom condition, with the factory carbon fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof showing no delamination and the Interlagos Blue metallic paint maintaining deep gloss. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach: rod bearings and throttle actuators have been preventatively replaced with documented service history. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers crisp, instantaneous gear changes, while the M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) ensure peak chassis composure. Riding on pristine Style 359M competition wheels with fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, this is a turn-key, concours-level specimen for the serious enthusiast.",
